{"tid":1961591,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果向中國捐 5000 萬人民幣 Tim Cook：中國應變力令人欽佩","createTime":"2020-04-07T01:42:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T05:49:18.000Z","uid":52215,"like":5,"dislike":119,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"58e8ab76eb2c8d89edde5cdaa9592502d48063ab","tid":1961591,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:42:29.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19）仍然蔓延全球，不少企業「轉行」製造口罩和抗疫物資，而蘋果也為中國、北美和歐洲三個疫症重災區捐款和捐贈物資。<br />\n<br />\nTim Cook 4 月 1 日用 iPhone 11 Pro Max 在微博發文，表示中國在武漢肺炎期間展示了令人欽佩的精神和應變能力，蘋果感謝團隊合作伙伴和客戶的支持，並已向中國扶貧基金會捐贈 5000 萬元人民幣，其中 2000 萬元人民幣是支持包括雷神山在內湖北地區的六家醫院，蘋果特別感謝中國以及世界各地的所有醫療響應者。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6q3PWU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6q3PWU.jpg&h=916db1d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7ad816a3b87d3422a7d0457db974678953c72653","tid":1961591,"uid":287269,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:43:47.000Z","msg":"中國每日得果幾單仲捐？"},{"pid":"370ca7eb915fcf0df7cb3e7c7e3e2de3673214c6","tid":1961591,"uid":187987,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"幾識玩，D小粉紅會唔會話改用iphone，唔用華為?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華為有冇捐過錢比中共??"},{"pid":"f5fb50963e583a2ba682bc4e3dc7f4f97a23cd65","tid":1961591,"uid":55533,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"370ca7eb915fcf0df7cb3e7c7e3e2de3673214c6","tid":1961591,"uid":187987,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:45:28.000Z","msg":"幾識玩，D小粉紅會唔會話改用iphone，唔用華為?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n華為有冇捐過錢比中共??"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:46:35.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n只係屌蘋果冇咁